{"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/537713467"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IrsvEnf6w9OQ6EAMaCDgxNzczODAwIJChopUGMAA4SUAvcgk1Mzc3MTM0Njd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1655392130.0252175", "card_id": "Q_525445417", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 143}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你认为游戏中该不该提供「自动战斗」、「自动采集」这类功能，影响总体而言是积极还是消极的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "一些游戏操作过于繁琐、重复，所以开发者会在其中增添诸如「自动战斗」、「自动采集」这样的功能。 这类功能释放了玩家的双手，可以使玩家在挂机同时做别的事情。但又是否会导致玩家认为游戏没什么可玩性呢？比如挂机挂着挂着就睡着了。 ———分割线——— 随着回答变多，我发现自动系统似乎有点「歧义」。此处问题提到的自动系统，指的是让计算机玩游戏的那类自动系统，也就是在计算机仍要执行手动操作时需要执行的部分，比如单次攻击、单次采集等。手动操作需要多长时间的，这类自动系统也需要多长时间。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-73d0dd27fc5a9a7cb718322f96f4d22b_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/525445417"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IrsvEnf6w9OQ6EAMaCDc5MDQ3MTY1IOuSm5IGMAg4uQFAMHIJNTI1NDQ1NDE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1655392130.025782", "card_id": "Q_537703665", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 135}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "想送自家闺女去学一门防身的武术，学什么有用?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-9f14dd6f59491da3561450ff6257da2d_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/537703665"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IrsvEnf6w9OQ6EAMaCDgxNzcxNTk2IPD5oZUGMAk4rQFAMXIJNTM3NzAzNjY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous": ""}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15}